# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# VoteWise — Environment Variables
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your Firebase project credentials.
#
# SECURITY: The .env file is git-ignored. NEVER commit real credentials.
#
# How to get these values:
#   1. Go to the Firebase Console: https://console.firebase.google.com
#   2. Select your project → Project Settings → General
#   3. Scroll down to "Your apps" → Web app → Config
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Firebase Configuration (required for all features)
VITE_FIREBASE_API_KEY=your-api-key-here
VITE_FIREBASE_AUTH_DOMAIN=your-project.firebaseapp.com
VITE_FIREBASE_PROJECT_ID=your-project-id
VITE_FIREBASE_STORAGE_BUCKET=your-project.appspot.com
VITE_FIREBASE_MESSAGING_SENDER_ID=000000000000
VITE_FIREBASE_APP_ID=1:000000000000:web:0000000000000000
VITE_FIREBASE_MEASUREMENT_ID=G-XXXXXXXXXX

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# IMPORTANT — Gemini API Key
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# The Gemini API key is NOT set here. It is stored ONLY in the
# Cloud Functions environment (server-side) and never exposed
# to the client bundle.
#
# To set it for Cloud Functions:
#   firebase functions:secrets:set GEMINI_API_KEY
#
# Or for local emulator testing:
#   Create functions/.env with: GEMINI_API_KEY=your-key
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
